@startuml baseline-sequence
!theme plain
title Sequence: Baseline Document Approved

participant "Document\nOwner" as Owner
participant "Baseline\nManager" as Baseline
participant "SRS\nParser" as Parser
participant "SRS\nOwner" as SRSOwner
participant "Document /\nVersion Control\nSystem" as DocSystem

Owner -> Baseline: submit baseline doc
Baseline -> Parser: extract requirements
Parser -> SRSOwner: generate suggestions
SRSOwner -> Parser: review & approve
Parser -> DocSystem: submit suggestions for review
SRSOwner -> DocSystem: approve and integrate suggestions
DocSystem -> Baseline: confirm SRS updated
Baseline -> Owner: notify "integrated"

alt Owner rejects
  SRSOwner -> Baseline: reject suggestions
  Baseline -> Owner: notify "rejected"
end

note over Parser
  Uses document master list
  "Impacts SRS?" co